$7.995 Million
2.2 Acres | 4 Bed | 6 Bath | 7 Car Garage + Lift

A Bold & Innovative Newly Built Estate, 15 Provence Court Is An Ultra-Luxe, Architectural Masterpiece Offering Inimitable Style, Scale, & Exquisite Design On Over 2 Acres. The Estate Boasts 4 Bedrooms, 6 Bathrooms, Including Dual Garages That Can House Up To 8 Cars. Surrounded By Magnificent Views, & Inspiring Quality, Residents Will Be Immersed In An Environment Of Creativity And Luxury. Welcome To A Truly Bespoke Lifestyle - A Once In A Lifetime Offering!

Visit 15PROVENCE.COM for more details.

Ramin Khaze @khaze.re
